Class FinalStatWriter

java.lang.Object
  contesttimer.FinalStatWriter

public class FinalStatWriter
extends java.lang.Object

An instance of class FinalStatWriter writes the current statistics of a programming contest to a comma separated value file (.csv) named ExitGameStats.csv. This file can be loaded into any spreadsheet. Teams appear in order by division.
